reviewText: I bought this for my sister. She loves it.

This movie was absolutely incredible! I shall watch it many times in order to capture the many loving nuances. I could not help but to say a prayer after crying through most of this heart-wrenching tale which leads to ever-lasting love between two precious souls. In my prayer I asked God why there are so many tragic human created events in our lives? The answer which came to me intuitively was that there are so many equally loving things which alter our lives eternally, all we have to do is seek these miracles. They are to be found by THE GRACE OF GOD.....

It's good movie especially when snowed in:)
